    <datafield tag="520" ind1=" " ind2=" ">
      <subfield code="a">Manual of arithmetic and geometry for merchants' use including how to calculate the area of a ship. According to the compiler, the work includes excerpts from the following texts: Muntakhab al-ḥisāb, Līlāvatī, and Dastūr al-ʻamal.</subfield>
    </datafield>
    <datafield tag="500" ind1=" " ind2=" ">
      <subfield code="a">Title from introduction (f. 2r).</subfield>
    </datafield>
    <datafield tag="541" ind1="1" ind2=" ">
      <subfield code="a">Gift of David Eugene Smith, 1931-1934.</subfield>
    </datafield>
    <datafield tag="500" ind1=" " ind2=" ">
      <subfield code="a">Layout: 15 long lines with some geometrical figures and formulas written vertically in between the text.</subfield>
    </datafield>
    <datafield tag="500" ind1=" " ind2=" ">
      <subfield code="a">Script: Written in rapid nastaʻliq in black ink; pointed, unvocalized.</subfield>
    </datafield>
    <datafield tag="500" ind1=" " ind2=" ">
      <subfield code="a">Decoration: Overlines, headings, and textual divisions in red. Geometrical diagrams in black.</subfield>
    </datafield>
    <datafield tag="545" ind1="0" ind2=" ">
      <subfield code="a">Author's name appears in the manuscript as Rajab ʻAlī Beg wald Fāz̤il Beg. The work is listed in Āghā Buzurg al-Ṭihrānī as number 215 (3.73). Author's name also listed in Fihris aʻlām al-Dharīʻah ilá taṣānīf al-Shīʻah as Ibn Rajab, ʻAbd al-Qāhir al-Ḥuwayzī al-ʻIbadi (1.852).</subfield>
    </datafield>
    <datafield tag="546" ind1=" " ind2=" ">
      <subfield code="a">Persian.</subfield>
    </datafield>
    <datafield tag="500" ind1=" " ind2=" ">
      <subfield code="a">Inserted: A letter written by David Eugene Smith on behalf of the American Mathematical Society (founded 1888) asking for contributions to the library of the Society laid in (between f. 5v and 6r). The back of the letter holds a handwritten long division problem, copied from f. 5v, with an explanation by Smith.</subfield>
    </datafield>
    <datafield tag="500" ind1=" " ind2=" ">
      <subfield code="a">Shelfmark: MS Or 36.</subfield>
    </datafield>
    <datafield tag="500" ind1=" " ind2=" ">
      <subfield code="a">Origin: Copy completed on 25 April 1851; the corresponding date in Vikram Samvat, 1908, is also given (f. 76v).</subfield>
    </datafield>
